38
00:04:20,970 --> 00:04:22,090
But I wanna help.

39
00:04:22,260 --> 00:04:25,360
I just don't know what to do to make you happy again.

40
00:04:27,110 --> 00:04:29,100
Then why don't you fight for a change?

41
00:04:34,990 --> 00:04:36,830
Wanna know what Kyubey told me?

42
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:39,400
You've got more potential than anyone.

43
00:04:39,710 --> 00:04:43,660
You could beat any witch [with] no problem
and you wouldn't even suffer like I do.

44
00:04:43,850 --> 00:04:44,720
But I...

45
00:04:46,410 --> 00:04:47,680
I just...

46
00:04:48,500 --> 00:04:53,050
If you really wanna help me, you should try
putting yourself in my shoes for a change.

47
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,850
But you can't.

48
00:04:55,300 --> 00:04:56,280
Of course not.

49
00:04:57,770 --> 00:05:00,970
