but "have to" has a slightly different vibe.

107
00:08:08,530 --> 00:08:09,230
For example...

108
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:10,760
Why did I let her go?

109
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,920
I should've gone after her.

110
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:25,770
Wait...

111
00:08:25,970 --> 00:08:28,540
I don't think I've ever seen you
walking home this way before.

112
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:29,940
How come?

113
00:08:30,470 --> 00:08:32,220
Did you just move or something?

114
00:08:32,700 --> 00:08:36,340
Actually, my house is in the exact opposite direction.

115
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:38,580
Okay...

116
00:08:38,770 --> 00:08:40,840
Then, why are you walking this way?

117
00:08:42,900 --> 00:08:44,050
