118
00:08:45,420 --> 00:08:47,630
There's something I've been wanting to tell you.

119
00:08:48,760 --> 00:08:50,080
She hasn't come home?

120
00:08:50,620 --> 00:08:51,820
Since yesterday?

121
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:53,480
