123
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:57,190
I understand.

124
00:08:57,970 --> 00:08:58,900
Okay.

125
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,780
Thank you very much.

126
00:09:11,830 --> 00:09:13,000
Sayaka...

127
00:09:13,590 --> 00:09:14,820
I've gotta find her!

128
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,920
Ahhhhh!

129
00:10:12,500 --> 00:10:13,970
Why can't you understand?

130
00:10:14,190 --> 00:10:16,160
You don't have the luxury to fool around.

131
00:10:16,620 --> 00:10:18,160
You should only hunt witches.

132
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:19,910
