137
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,440
What is this?

138
00:10:36,570 --> 00:10:37,670
What are you up to?

139
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:39,920
Don't be stupid.

140
00:10:41,540 --> 00:10:43,510
You're in no position to question my help.

141
00:10:43,970 --> 00:10:46,190
Or, do you just hate the idea of it?

142
00:10:46,850 --> 00:10:50,000
I'm gonna be a different kind of magical girl.

143
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:51,870
That's what I decided.

144
00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:55,970
