171
00:12:04,380 --> 00:12:06,420
Everything has to do with her.

172
00:12:14,250 --> 00:12:15,140
You're sharp.

173
00:12:15,730 --> 00:12:16,310
Yes.

174
00:12:16,420 --> 00:12:17,420
You're right about me.

175
00:12:17,810 --> 00:12:19,890
I don't give a damn if you live or die.

176
00:12:20,010 --> 00:12:20,860
I don't care.

177
00:12:21,020 --> 00:12:24,690
I just don't want Madoka to see you like
this, as you destroy yourself.

178
00:12:25,730 --> 00:12:28,950
If you don't let me help you now,
you're going to die, either way.

179
00:12:29,290 --> 00:12:32,550
You see, if you make her suffer anymore,

180
00:12:33,750 --> 00:12:34,930
then I will...

181
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,080
